data.text:
Treat yourself to a sturdy hand-sewn tote bag to keep all your birthy essentials when visiting clients, featuring my 'Journey from Womb to World' map.

Made from tear-resistant fabric, my large womb to world tote bag is robust and durable. With its comfortable fabric handles and generous capacity, it's here to make plastic bags a thing of the past - and help advertise your supreme birth-nerd-iness to all the world!

Black double carry handles

Section of the map printed on one side only, reverse is plain fabric

Solvent-free eco-friendly production

To keep the design looking bold, washing is not recommended.

Dimensions - Width: 40cm x Height 42cm (plus handles)
